{"tid":1513685,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳盧卡古哀求山神投國米","createTime":"2019-08-28T12:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T12:30:04.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f01805a8746e14408bcd69c61bd2e475178c89","tid":1513685,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:21:57.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼聯前鋒阿歷斯山齊士即將轉投國際米蘭，早就從紅變藍黑的射手盧卡古也有功勞。<br />\n<br />\n阿歷斯山齊士（Alexis Sanchez）即將由曼聯借到國際米蘭，與前紅魔隊友盧卡古再度合作，齊齊轉戰意甲。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒披露，比利時前鋒盧卡古之前與山齊士通過幾次電話，促成了今次轉會；前者甚至哀求山神一起去國米。據知，盧卡古告訴山齊士，米蘭城風景優美，令人一見難忘。<br />\n<br />\n盧卡古對山神所說的，不僅是國米的戰略計劃，更重要是意大利的生活模式，比起曼徹斯特的鄰居更加優雅，更加宜室宜居。或許因為生活更好，盧卡古在意甲地標戰便取得入球。<br />\n<br />\n山神自阿仙奴加盟紅魔後，表現大走樣，上陣45場，僅入5球，被棄用是眾望所歸。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"052d75f5050c53f43080c12d334db3819e298a89","tid":1513685,"uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/NINTCHDBPICT000380292626.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FNINTCHDBPICT000380292626.jpg&h=435cd82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山神曼聯highlight"},{"pid":"16b0a008282dd35220a9cbdd2ddfffdd1b18f8bd","tid":1513685,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5LYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=9213350f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n90